Class ClassShape

java.lang.Object
org.example.my_project.Models.Shape
org.example.my_project.Models.ClassShape
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ClassShape extends Shape implements Serializable
The ClassShape class represents a shape used to depict a class or interface in a UML-like diagram. It extends the abstract Shape class and provides additional functionalities for managing attributes, methods, associations, and inheritance/implementation relationships.

This class implements Serializable to support object serialization.
